564
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:28,960
Yao,

565
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:30,980
the sunshine outside is lovely.

566
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,650
Do you want to go out for a walk?

567
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,500
No, Fuyi.

568
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:35,890
I'm feeling a bit tired.

569
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:37,820
Did you not sleep well?

570
00:33:38,080 --> 00:33:40,210
Shall I make some jujube soup for you?

571
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,540
No need.

572
00:33:41,930 --> 00:33:42,770
Thank you.

573
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:47,300
You rest early.

574
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:48,600
I won't disturb you.

575
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:49,690
If you need me,

576
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:50,930
just let me know.

577
00:33:58,990 --> 00:33:59,830
Cultivator Mu,

578
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:02,370
the matter you asked me to investigate

579
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,020
has some leads now.

580
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,120
Cultivator Mu,

581
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:10,600
here.

582
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:19,650
Cultivator Mu,

583
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:22,210
the task you gave me is done.

584
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:25,670
The great fire at Xingshan Hall
ten years ago

585
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:29,100
was announced as an accidental fire.

586
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:31,760
However, after my painstaking efforts

587
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,330
and tireless work day and night,

588
00:34:33,990 --> 00:34:35,610
I have found out.

589
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:37,670
Just as you suspected,

590
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:38,900
the great fire is

591
00:34:39,470 --> 00:34:43,810
closely related to the Dowager Consort.

592
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:46,460
The Princess's possession was feigned.

593
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,760
But Empress Dowager Zhao

594
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,980
insisted it was caused by a demon.

595
00:34:50,470 --> 00:34:52,060
There must be a hidden truth behind this.

596
00:34:53,560 --> 00:34:55,020
Since you have discovered some clues,

597
00:34:55,330 --> 00:34:57,770
why are you hiding it from Fuyi
and telling me privately?

598
00:34:59,720 --> 00:35:03,030
Because this matter concerns
your ancestor,

599
00:35:03,030 --> 00:35:05,400
I think it's better to

600
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,250
talk to you alone first.

601
00:35:06,590 --> 00:35:07,540
My ancestor?

602
00:35:08,720 --> 00:35:11,130
Your father, Mu Huaijiang.

603
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:21,940
Does liking someone

604
00:35:22,830 --> 00:35:24,250
necessarily mean you have to express it

605
00:35:24,770 --> 00:35:25,940
and be together?

606
00:35:26,470 --> 00:35:27,310
Yes.

607
00:35:29,750 --> 00:35:32,760
How difficult it is to bring two people

608
00:35:32,770 --> 00:35:34,660
who like each other together?

609
00:35:34,970 --> 00:35:35,900
It's like someone

610
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:38,370
has already led you
to the gates of paradise,

611
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:41,650
and you just need to open the door
to find happiness,

612
00:35:42,110 --> 00:35:44,110
but if you shrink back out of fear,

613
00:35:44,110 --> 00:35:45,420
what a pity that would be!

614
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:11,220
(Bustling and Crowded)

615
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:14,060
Local specialties?

616
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:16,140
Yes.

617
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:19,480
I want to buy some local specialties
for my grandfather

618
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,940
