622
00:36:26,550 --> 00:36:27,390
So,

623
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:29,730
I need to buy it now.

624
00:36:30,130 --> 00:36:31,100
When I meet him,

625
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:32,420
