626
00:36:33,990 --> 00:36:35,170
That's right.

627
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,120
Alright.

628
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:38,130
Let's go.

629
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,500
Go.

630
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:42,840
