648
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,730
Miss Lin and I

649
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,980
are truly destined to meet.

650
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,590
Come on, move everything inside
and set it up.

651
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:34,430
Hurry up.

652
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:36,730
Take it slow.

653
